==English==
===Etymology===
Probably from or akin to Old English ''[[drūsian]]''
===Adjective===
'''drowsy'''

#Inclined to drowse; heavy with sleepiness; lethargic; dozy.
#Disposing to sleep; lulling; soporific.
#Dull; stupid.

